{"tid":2414444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港人死都唔想用安心出行應用程式姐","createTime":"2021-02-19T11:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T23:09:12.000Z","uid":44367,"like":96,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"398f45e068b4cfa18e0fc187abcb82aabf0c8b3b","tid":2414444,"uid":44367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:38:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">因為我地香港人從來都唔撚係靠你港共啊柒頭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n武漢一話封關開始香港人就完全靠自己<br />\n去日本去泰國去英國撲口罩防疫物資<br />\n個陣你垃圾港共重叫人唔洗戴口罩戴左都要除返落黎咋碌柒<br />\n<br />\n依家唔係有口罩令分分鐘無人戴添<br />\n你重搞乜鳩安心出行彩你都有味啦<br />\n鎖區洗樓大海撈針 大陸閪自出自入<br />\n要七百幾萬人陪你搵個七百幾萬分之幾個人出黎<br />\n搞到好似世界末日咁  嚇鬼啊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我同你講香港人無人驚啊<br />\n共產黨殺到黎唔驚驚區區幾個武漢肺炎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我地香港人係唔撚會用安心出行<br />\n亦唔撚會打大陸疫苗啊傻閪</span></span>"},{"pid":"16ee1ce80cd98e40005c513d526cf76ac8ab7faf","tid":2414444,"uid":347528,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"我有用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5736407eeea8e07e9036e6d3d3bc75377fcc0c26","tid":2414444,"uid":147770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:40:38.000Z","msg":"根本連d藍店都覺得個app煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母習近平<br />\n拉尻我呀笨"},{"pid":"3263a9c94b1cba574532395d74ebfc65454dfdaa","tid":2414444,"uid":295481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大把方法唔用唔明點解個個仆去用"},{"pid":"8fb4faaf200517e7567e3f00cc35292553f2d06f","tid":2414444,"uid":44367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:43:55.000Z","msg":"聽你港共講香港人晨早死撚左啦<br />\n<br />\n洗撚用你啲濕鳩「防疫」方法咩<br />\n<br />\n淨係堂食先有武肺 信你班柒頭真係on9<br 